Andre Wink does not specify that he was a Pashtun, but says he was "probably an Afghan," and the statement currently given does not follow this lack of certainty given by Andre Wink. The previous sources which were misleadingly erased said that there was no definitive origin of Hasan Gangu, which should be restored.
